{"tid":1348074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（慎入）16歲示威者眼部中16發橡膠子彈致盲","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:29:15.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e53ad33d6ce8a928c91e4c9902cc5f9897891214","tid":1348074,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉近日一宗遊行示威爆發成警民衝突，警方於無預警下進行暴力鎮壓，警員向民眾發射了多枚橡膠子彈，其中一名委內瑞拉青年身中52槍，當中16發子彈射中眼部引致失明，委內瑞拉政府最後宣布起訴兩名涉事警員，「殺人未遂」、「不當使用武器」、「殘忍行為」等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nljqqXnngRgzbS44NDTk8Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/orientalsundayent.com/9ffbce78df771bfec45807e47b7f89fc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnljqqXnngRgzbS44NDTk8Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F9ffbce78df771bfec45807e47b7f89fc&h=905fa0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方無預警下進行武力鎮壓 委內瑞拉青年眼部中16發橡膠子彈致盲<br />\n7月2日委內瑞拉的聖克里斯托瓦爾市（San Cristobal）有民眾上街示威，抗議當地的家用煤氣短缺，但最終演變成警民衝突。警方在無預警的情況下對市民進行暴力鎮壓，發射多枚橡膠子彈，其中一名16歲的男青年示威者Rufo Chacon，全身慘中52發，當中16發子彈擊中眼部致盲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Gs2mEUvBhYxzZ0i27sizBA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/orientalsundayent.com/d9ad952c3516816768a5eeb90f1bda66\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGs2mEUvBhYxzZ0i27sizBA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fd9ad952c3516816768a5eeb90f1bda66&h=7b29b502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRufo Chacon馬上緊急送院，雖然醫生能把眼部的子彈碎片取出來，但也有部分留在腦內及臉部，還有感染的風險。而他的14歲弟弟Adrian頭部也被警察用警棍擊中，他們二人當日是跟著媽媽一同上街示威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9DHtUeuDCQInZmKr1BdtFw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/orientalsundayent.com/7395dc8b5f1bad3bcd30205bf5e8e884\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9DHtUeuDCQInZmKr1BdtFw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F7395dc8b5f1bad3bcd30205bf5e8e884&h=5a6c2bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後警方發出了一份調查報告，指出當日有警員沒有在預警的情況下使用武力，除了Rufo Chacon及弟弟Adrian外，也有另一名未成年者在示威中受到傷害。聯合國人權事務高級專員Michelle Bachelet隨後發出了聲明，指責委內瑞拉政府的行為「違反人權」。最終政府宣布對2名涉事警員作出起訴，分別控告「殺人未遂」、「不當使用武器」、「殘忍行為」等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n但是委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅（Nicolas Maduro）卻反指調查報告並不公正，存有偏見。Rufo Chacon示威後表示：「政治家全部都是騙子，這裡的法律是用來攻擊人民，並不是保護他們。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ybzSASb2D_SYsybauR82bA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/orientalsundayent.com/96ccd3d907a74299e452a3f47723732e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FybzSASb2D_SYsybauR82bA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F96ccd3d907a74299e452a3f47723732e&h=7d329e4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"508447b8f9c3a7fc3423a9ff38f4a07bf134a1f7","tid":1348074,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5849798aab7a28e5872107c1b364422e2c30395","tid":1348074,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"屌。。。。眼罩好緊要！！！"}]}